        <p>You'll continue to receive our latest updates, news, and exclusive content.</p>
      {{else}}
        <p>Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p>Get ready to receive our latest updates, news, and exclusive content directly to your inbox.</p>
      {{/if}}
      
      <p>Here's what you can expect from us:</p>
